{"data":[{"date":"09:04 20/07","title":"\u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t c\u1ef1c n\u1eb7ng v\u00ec h\u00e0nh vi c\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed3","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/dong-doi-cua-duc-chinh-nhan-an-phat-cuc-nang-vi-hanh-vi-con-do.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a L\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t cho c\u00e1c l\u1ed7i t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 19 V-League, trong \u0111\u00f3 ri\u00eang th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n L\u00ea V\u0103n H\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t r\u1ea5t n\u1eb7ng.</h2><h2>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n L\u00ea V\u0103n H\u01b0ng nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t c\u1ef1c n\u1eb7ng v\u00ec h\u00e0nh vi c\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed3</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 19 V-League, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n L\u00ea V\u0103n H\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh vi r\u1ea5t ph\u1ea3n c\u1ea3m khi \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0o l\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Matias Nicolas Jadue Gonzales c\u1ee7a CLB b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TP.H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u00e0y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t r\u1ea5t n\u1eb7ng. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 19/7/2018, Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam (VFF) \u0111\u00e3 ban h\u00e0nh c\u00e1c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh\u00a0x\u1eed ph\u1ea1t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y hai m\u01b0\u01a1i tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00ecnh ch\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u 04 tr\u1eadn k\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i V-League.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n L\u00ea V\u0103n H\u01b0ng nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t c\u1ef1c n\u1eb7ng v\u00ec h\u00e0nh vi c\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n L\u00ea V\u0103n H\u01b0ng nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t c\u1ef1c n\u1eb7ng v\u00ec h\u00e0nh vi c\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/dong-doi-cua-duc-chinh-nhan-an-phat-cuc-nang-vi-hanh-vi-con-do.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n L\u00ea V\u0103n H\u01b0ng b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 t\u1edbi 4 tr\u1eadn v\u00ec h\u00e0nh vi c\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed3</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t gi\u00e0nh cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n V\u0103n H\u01b0ng th\u00ec l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n CLB SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng \u00f4ng\u00a0B\u00f9i Xu\u00e2n H\u00f2a c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t 5 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng, \u0111\u00ecnh ch\u1ec9 02 tr\u1eadn\u00a0do c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh vi ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa hai CLB b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng v\u00e0 TP.H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh. B\u1ed1n th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a CLB SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng ch\u1ec9 nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t c\u1ea3nh c\u00e1o nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf g\u1ed3m l\u00e0 tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd Nguy\u1ec5n Minh D\u0169ng, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Minh Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o vi\u00ean Nguy\u1ec5n Qu\u1ed1c H\u00f9ng v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 M\u1ea1c \u0110\u1ee9c Vi\u1ec7t Anh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i L\u00ea V\u0103n H\u01b0ng th\u00ec m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t sau v\u00f2ng 19 V-League l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Patiyo Tambwe c\u1ee7a XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 do c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh vi c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh x\u00e2m ph\u1ea1m th\u00e2n th\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Zeba Josip c\u1ee7a HAGL trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i Pleiku. Patiyo s\u1ebd b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t m\u01b0\u1eddi l\u0103m tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00ecnh ch\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u 03 tr\u1eadn k\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mi\u1ec1n T\u00e2y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, BTC tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t ti\u1ec1n 70 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng do \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ed1t ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng trong s\u00e2n; n\u00e9m nhi\u1ec1u chai n\u01b0\u1edbc, v\u1eadt l\u1ea1 xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n, kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 ch\u1ea1y xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 mang b\u0103ng r\u00f4n c\u00f3 n\u1ed9i dung kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u00e0o s\u00e2n. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00eda Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t 40 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng do C\u0110V \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u00f3 c\u00e1c h\u00e0nh vi: \u0111\u1ed1t ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng trong s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng; n\u00e9m nhi\u1ec1u chai n\u01b0\u1edbc, v\u1eadt l\u1ea1 xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n; ch\u1ea1y v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 mang b\u0103ng r\u00f4n c\u00f3 n\u1ed9i dung kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u00e0o s\u00e2n.\u00a0<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4410","checkdouble":"191643"},{"date":"09:31 20/07","title":"Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng V-League thay t\u01b0\u1edbng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/1/26/them-mot-doi-bong-vleague-thay-tuong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 20 V-League 2018, CLB XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thay HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng khi \u0111\u01b0a \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n Thanh Danh l\u00ean thay HLV \u0110inh H\u1ed3ng Vinh.</h2><h2>XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 thay HLV \u0110inh H\u1ed3ng Vinh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 thay HLV \u0110inh H\u1ed3ng Vinh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 thay HLV \u0110inh H\u1ed3ng Vinh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/1/26/xac-nhan-nguoi-thay-the-hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-tai-u19-viet-nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV \u0110inh H\u1ed3ng Vinh th\u00f4i d\u1eabn d\u1eaft CLB XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1\u00a0</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay, d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i \u0110inh H\u1ed3ng Vinh, CLB XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i nh\u1ecf nhuy\u1ec5n, kh\u00e1 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y lu\u00f4n g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong t\u1ed1p 5 tr\u00ean BXH.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u ch\u1eefng l\u1ea1i \u1edf gi\u1eefa m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u00e0 cho t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y, khi m\u00e0 V-League 2018 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 7 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eefa s\u1ebd k\u1ebft th\u00fac, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mi\u1ec1n T\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ee5t xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 13 tr\u00ean BXH. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 nguy hi\u1ec3m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh n\u00e0y, BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Thanh Danh v\u00e0o gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng, thay cho HLV \u0110inh H\u1ed3ng Vinh. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, \u00f4ng\u00a0Nguy\u1ec5n Thanh Danh kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 xa l\u1ea1 v\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 b\u1edfi \u00f4ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y th\u0103ng h\u1ea1ng n\u0103m 2015. Sau \u0111\u00f3, v\u1ecb n\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m vai tr\u00f2 Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 T\u00e2y \u0110\u00f4.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng Vinh s\u1ebd tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mi\u1ec1n T\u00e2y t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng 20 V-League. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i sau 19 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u, CLB b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 x\u1ebfp v\u1ecb tr\u00ed 13/14 \u0111\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i, h\u1ecd \u0111ang c\u00f3 (17 \u0111i\u1ec3m). X\u1ebfp ngay sau h\u1ecd l\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC (16 \u0111i\u1ec3m), \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 20 v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 20/07. Vi\u1ec7c thay t\u01b0\u1edbng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 thi \u0111\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<span style=\"font-size:\n16.0pt;line-height:115%\"> <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4409","checkdouble":"191649"},{"date":"09:53 20/07","title":"HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ec9 ra \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/hlv-park-hang-seo-chi-ra-diem-yeu-cua-cau-thu-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn s\u1ee9c \u00e9p gh\u00ea g\u1edbm tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018, HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ec9 ra \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00ean danh s\u00e1ch 30 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018, HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n sau v\u00f2ng 20 V-League 2018. HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng n\u1eeda th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi g\u00fat l\u1ea1i danh s\u00e1ch nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Park Hang Seo chi ra diem yeu cua cau thu Viet Nam de chan thuong.\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ec9 ra \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ec5 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/hlv-park-hang-seo-chi-ra-diem-yeu-cua-cau-thu-viet-nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ec9 ra \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ec5 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng tr\u1edf ng\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Park Hang Seo chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean Thanh Ni\u00ean r\u1eb1ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe v\u1eabn khi\u1ebfn \u00f4ng lo l\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t: &quot;C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam r\u1ea5t hay b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u01a1 h\u00e1ng, c\u01a1 \u0111\u00f9i m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n do t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t v\u00e0 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c ch\u01b0a th\u1eadt t\u1ed1t, v\u00ec v\u1eady \u0111\u1ec3 chinh ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ec9nh cao nh\u01b0 ASIAD, ngo\u00e0i b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh, s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ecfe \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u00f2n ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ASIAD 2018 s\u1ebd kh\u00f3 h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m. \u00d4ng ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n s\u1ebd tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp th\u00eam 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i n\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t.</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ecbu \u00e1p l\u1ef1c l\u1edbn<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Park Hang Seo th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu \u00e1p l\u1ef1c &quot;r\u1ea5t kinh kh\u1ee7ng&quot; v\u00ec th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n k\u1ef3 t\u00edch \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 khi\u1ebfn th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo g\u1eb7p \u00e1p l\u1ef1c v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bang dau cua DT Olympic Viet Nam tai ASIAD 2018.\" title=\"B\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/bang-asiad.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>B\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ea7y Park cho bi\u1ebft m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1eabn l\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang c\u00f3 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, Pakistan v\u00e0 Nepal. Tuy nhi\u00ean, AFC \u0111ang y\u00eau c\u1ea7u ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n l\u1ea1i l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m khi \u0111\u1ec3... s\u00f3t hai \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n UAE v\u00e0 Palestine.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 x\u00e1o tr\u1ed9n, nh\u1eefng k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch th\u1ea7y Park \u0111\u1eb7t ra s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-dat-muc-tieu-cho-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018-168-191537.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tien-dung-thua-nhan-kho-canh-tranh-voi-van-lam-tai-asiad-2018-168-191517.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-le-thuy-hai-noi-gi-ve-danh-sach-tap-trung-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-191477.html\">HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 danh s\u00e1ch t\u1eadp trung \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-guong-mat-bi-hlv-park-hang-seo-bo-quen-tai-asiad-2018-168-191462.html\">Nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t b\u1ecb HLV Park Hang Seo &lsquo;b\u1ecf qu\u00ean&rsquo; t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-bu-tottenham-canh-tranh-hcv-asiad-cung-lua-cong-phuong-168-191451.html\">Sao b\u1ef1 Tottenham c\u1ea1nh tranh HCV ASIAD c\u00f9ng l\u1ee9a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-tu-danh-sach-trieu-tap-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018-168-191444.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec t\u1eeb danh s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)&nbsp;</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4408","checkdouble":"191650"},{"date":"10:49 20/07","title":"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng 20 V-League: \u0110\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn SLNA \u2013 HAGL","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/10/14/truoc-vong-20-vleague-dai-chien-slna-hagl.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 20 V-League 2018, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111ang d\u1ed3n s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa SLNA vs HAGL, hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb r\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</h2><h2>\u0110\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn SLNA &ndash; HAGL<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00f2ng 20 V-League, CLB HAGL s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c mang t\u00ean SLNA tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Vinh. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu h\u00fat s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a NHM b\u1edfi c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi c\u00f9ng l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng s\u1eafc n\u00e9t, \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">SLNA v\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u b\u1edfi su\u1ed1t 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e3 to\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Vinh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 v\u1eady, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y c\u0169ng h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chu\u1ed7i 7 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng 13 cho t\u1edbi nay. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap SLNA c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 th\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng 4 tr\u00ean BXH.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng 20 V-League \u0110\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn SLNA &ndash; HAGL h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng 20 V-League \u0110\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn SLNA &ndash; HAGL h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/10/14/truoc-tran-hagl-vs-slna-chuyen-gia-mach-nuoc-cho-doi-bong-xu-nghe.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>&nbsp;SLNA vs HAGL l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ea1i&nbsp;v\u00f2ng 20 V-League</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda HAGL, h\u1ecd th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 &lsquo;y\u1ebfu b\u00f3ng v\u00eda&rsquo; khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u xa nh\u00e0. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u00fang \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y khi &lsquo;G\u1ed7&rsquo; t\u1eebng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Thanh H\u00f3a hay b\u1ecb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam, Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t SLNA ch\u1ec9 &lsquo;\u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00e2n, \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u1ea1ng&rsquo;, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i trong l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m m\u1eb7t s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. H\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, HAGL \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i SLNA v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-0. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u00eam t\u1ef1 tin trong l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Chung k\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 g\u1eb7p S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i quan tr\u1ecdng t\u1edbi t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 sau giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 nh\u01b0 &ldquo;hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng&rdquo; c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u00ec l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang sa s\u00fat sau chu\u1ed7i 10 tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 d\u1eabn t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 13 tr\u00ean BXH v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng h\u01a1n C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ebft b\u00e1t v\u00e0 x\u1ebfp \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u00ean BXH. Do \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u chi\u1ec1u nay, XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 ti\u1ebfp s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00ed nh\u01b0 &ldquo;chung k\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1ee3c&rdquo; c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">CLB XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 hi\u1ec7n nay \u0111ang x\u1ebfp tr\u00ean S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC, v\u1edbi kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00fang 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m (17 so v\u1edbi 16). V\u00ec th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn b\u1ee9t l\u00ean kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u00e1y BXH. Tuy nhi\u00ean trong t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n nay, r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng khi m\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 &ldquo;l\u1ea5n&rdquo; \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00e1ch.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Can Tho vs Sai Gon\" title=\"C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/nhan-dinh-can-tho-vs-sai-gon-17h00-ngay-207-vleague-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Thanh H\u00f3a c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f2i n\u1ee3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch V-League n\u0103m nay g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u00e3 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i khi l\u00fac n\u00e0y h\u1ecd v\u1eabn b\u1ecf xa \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 hai l\u00e0 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a t\u1edbi 14 \u0111i\u1ec3m. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 v\u00ec v\u1eady, n\u1ebfu ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc FLC Thanh H\u00f3a \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi th\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y l\u00ean ng\u00f4i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 b\u1ecb ch\u1eadm l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat so v\u1edbi d\u1ef1 t\u00ednh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c r\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111u\u1ed5i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u1edbi 7 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi t\u1ea1i H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby. Thanh H\u00f3a l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Tr\u1ecdng Ho\u00e0ng tuy nhi\u00ean H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c sau nh\u1eefng pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a d\u00e0n sao tr\u1ebb Quang H\u1ea3i, V\u0103n Ki\u00ean, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng v\u00e0 Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng V\u0103n Th\u00e1i Qu\u00fd.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thanh hoa vs Ha Noi\" title=\"thanh h\u00f3a vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/anh1_1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>&nbsp;H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Thanh H\u00f3a \u1edf 3 m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec v\u1eady, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Thanh \u0111ang r\u1ea5t n\u00f4n n\u00f3ng \u0111\u00f2i n\u1ee3 \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1. D\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng, Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh. 7 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft m\u00f9i chi\u1ebfn b\u1ea1i sau 5 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 2 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, d\u00f9 \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n nh\u00e0 b\u1ea7u Hi\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong c\u00e1c chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi Thanh H\u00f3a trong 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 0-3 ngay \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2016. V\u00ec th\u1ebf \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi h\u1ecd \u1edf tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean, v\u00f2ng 20 V-League 2018 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 c\u00e1c c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng vs \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng, Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh vs Qu\u1ea3ng Nam, Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng v\u00e0 CLB TP.HCM vs Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bongda24h s\u1ebd c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd theo d\u00f5i.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lich thi dau vong 20 V-League 2018\" title=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 20 V-League 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/Vong-20-V-League.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 20 V-League 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/nhan-dinh-bong-da/nhan-dinh-can-tho-vs-sai-gon-17h00-ngay-207-vleague-2018-344-191652.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/nhan-dinh-can-tho-vs-sai-gon-17h00-ngay-207-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/nhan-dinh-bong-da/nhan-dinh-can-tho-vs-sai-gon-17h00-ngay-207-vleague-2018-344-191652.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 17h00 ng\u00e0y 20/7 (V-League 2018)</span><br>\r\nC\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n l\u00fac 17h00 ng\u00e0y 20/7 (V\u00f2ng 20 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n,...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4407","checkdouble":"191655"},{"date":"09:06 20/07","title":"Real Madrid v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Neymar","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/8/6/real-madrid-van-con-co-hoi-chieu-mo-neymar.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid mua Neymar th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, theo \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh n\u1ebfu Los Blancos \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Neymar thay Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRonaldo \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay Real Madrid sau 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1985 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, anh \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Juventus.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Real Madrid mua Neymar \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Real Madrid mua Neymar \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/12/Co-hoi-de-Real-Madrid-mua-Neymar-o-He-2018-la-van-con-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real mu\u1ed1n mua Neymar thay Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, CR7 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat s\u1ed1 1 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Real. S\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng m\u00eanh m\u00f4ng tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Los Blancos. Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Real Madrid, Florentino Perez \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/nong-real-madrid-du-chi-hon-400-trieu-usd-de-mua-neymar-180-188194.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real quan t\u00e2m Neymar</span> c\u1ee7a PSG, h\u1ecd cho r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o cho Ronaldo. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn PSG t\u1eeb Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 222 tri\u1ec7u euro, b\u1edfi v\u1eady \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n Los Blancos s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, Real c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi 290 tri\u1ec7u euro mua si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i, h\u1ecd kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Real mua Neymar v\u1eabn c\u00f2n</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid mua Neymar th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, theo \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh n\u1ebfu Los Blancos \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Neymar PSG\" title=\"Neymar PSG\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/17/psg-neymar-da-dua-ra-quyet-dinh-ve-tuong-lai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i mua Neymar&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edd b\u00e1o c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Mundo Deportivo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh HLV Thomas Tuchel kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef Neymar b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1. \u00d4ng n\u00e0y ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec3 thu v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 qua \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 kh\u00e1c.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPSG coi Kylian Mbappe l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Neymar \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1998 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh trung t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u0169ng theo Mundo Deportivo, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 310 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng chi \u0111\u1eadm mua Neymar, Real s\u1ebd d\u1ed3n to\u00e0n l\u1ef1c mua Eden Hazard.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4406","checkdouble":"191642"},{"date":"11:37 20/07","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 20/07","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/20/chuyen-nhuong-real-madrid-hot-nhat-ngay-2007.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a Los Blancos \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 20/07.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Eden Hazard</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 2007 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 2007 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/Chuyen-nhuong-Real-Madrid-2018-hot-nhat-ngay-2007-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho Eden Hazard v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 125 tri\u1ec7u euro</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTheo Don Balon, chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Eden Hazard, the \u0111\u00f3 Los Blancos ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 125 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Gareth Bale s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Bernabeu ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c n\u1ebfu...</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Marca, Gareth Bale s\u1ebd ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c r\u1eddi Bernabeu n\u1ebfu Real mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. Hi\u1ec7n K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng \u0111ang nh\u1eafm Mbappe, Neymar v\u00e0 Hazard \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n mang Marcelo t\u1edbi Juventus</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin mua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Marcelo c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. \u0110\u1ed9i \u0110KV\u0110 Serie A c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi t\u1edbi 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i mua Mauro Icardi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 2007 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 2007 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/22/Chuyen-nhuong-Real-Madrid-2018-hot-nhat-ngay-2007-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mauro Icardi gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Inter Milan</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mauro Icardi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Inter Milan, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u ch\u1ea5m h\u1ebft cho tham v\u1ecdng s\u1edf h\u1eefu ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina c\u1ee7a Real Madrid.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Thibaut Courtois</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Daily Mail kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Real \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Thibaut Courtois v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u euro, vi\u1ec7c h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Los Blancos kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i chi qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Kovacic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Don Balon, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-het-gia-khong-tuong-cho-mateo-kovacic-180-191234.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real Madrid ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kovacic </span>n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, hi\u1ec7n Man City, MU v\u00e0 Tottenham l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Lucas Vazquez</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Vazquez gap kho o tran Real vs Bayern\" title=\"Vazquez gap kho o tran Real vs Bayern\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/2/Benzema-tran-Real-vs-Bayern-Chu-chim-trong-truyen-thuyet-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Vazquez\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Lucas Vazquez, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00e2n HLV Lopetegui kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n Los Blancos b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u1edf l\u1ea1i b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Anthony Martial b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Real</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Mirror, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Anthony Martial c\u1ee7a M.U b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Real. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Old Trafford, song Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ebfn 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4405","checkdouble":"191661"},{"date":"09:36 20/07","title":"Sao kh\u1ee7ng Chelsea b\u00e1o tin c\u1ef1c vui cho MU v\u00e0 Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/21/willian-bao-tin-cuc-vui-cho-mu-va-barca.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Willian r\u1eddi Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 \u0111ang l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, theo The Sun ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1eb7p BL\u0110 The Blues \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU v\u00e0 Barca mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Willian</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Willian l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Chelsea. D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean song hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 m\u00e0 anh th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. M\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i anh ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh 20 l\u1ea7n \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh nh\u01b0ng ghi 6 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 7 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca v\u00e0 MU ch\u00fa \u00fd Willian r\u1eddi Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Barca v\u00e0 MU ch\u00fa \u00fd Willian r\u1eddi Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/Barca-va-MU-chu-y-Willian-roi-Chelsea-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU v\u00e0 Barcar\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Willian</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 m\u00e0 Willian lu\u00f4n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh hay v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 khi\u1ebfn Mourinho th\u00e8m kh\u00e1t. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n MU mua Willian, c\u1ef1u HLV Chelsea mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p tr\u00f2 c\u0169 \u1edf s\u00e2n Old Trafford.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Willian, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng song b\u1ecb Chelsea t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u1eefa tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0ng The Blues v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/day-danh-sach-2-cau-thu-ma-hlv-sarri-muon-chelsea-giu-bang-duoc-172-190884.html\" target=\"_blank\">HLV Maurizio Sarri mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef Willian \u1edf l\u1ea1i</span>, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil. C\u1ef1u HLV Napoli mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 Chelsea gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Willian v\u00e0 Eden Hazard.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Willian b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Willian r\u1eddi Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 \u0111ang l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, theo The Sun ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1eb7p BL\u0110 The Blues \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sao kh\u1ee7ng Chelsea b\u00e1o tin c\u1ef1c vui cho MU v\u00e0 Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Sao kh\u1ee7ng Chelsea b\u00e1o tin c\u1ef1c vui cho MU v\u00e0 Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/5/Sao-khung-Chelsea-bao-tin-cuc-vui-cho-MU-va-Barca-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Willian b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Sarri \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Willian v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i. Theo The Sun s\u1edf d\u0129 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi&nbsp;Stamford Bridge b\u1edfi anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a Chelsea m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nWillian lo ng\u1ea1i r\u1eb1ng HLV Sarri kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Chelsea gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn, anh c\u0169ng \u0111ang th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a The Blues nh\u01b0 Hazard hay Courtois \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Stamford Bridge \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Real.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPhilippe Coutinho, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Willian \u1edf Barca \u0111ang ra s\u1ee9c thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i t\u1edbi Barca, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 M.U c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. N\u1ebfu M.U v\u00e0 Barca th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4404","checkdouble":"191646"},{"date":"10:38 20/07","title":"L\u1ed9 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 c\u1ef1c s\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a HLV Wenger","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/4/lo-ben-do-cuc-soc-cua-hlv-wenger.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Arsene Wenger d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ef1u HLV Arsenal.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Wenger</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau khi chia tay Arsenal sau h\u01a1n 20 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3, HLV Wenger v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o d\u00f9 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi m\u1eddi. D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 68 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed1n gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"R\u1eddi Arsenal, HLV Arsene Wenger d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"R\u1eddi Arsenal, HLV Arsene Wenger d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/4/lo-ben-do-cuc-soc-cua-hlv-wenger.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Wenger v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed1n gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. Theo Daily Mail, Arsene Wenger d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ef1u HLV Arsenal.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 4 n\u0103m nay, \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sa th\u1ea3i HLV Vahid Halilhodzic (ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bosnia) v\u00e0 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Akira Nishino. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y 63 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf hoa Anh \u0111\u00e0o v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u1edf World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u00f2n d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0, song c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i 3-2. D\u00f9 sao th\u00ec th\u00e0nh t\u00edch v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng 1/8 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 Akira Nishino \u0111ang l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, song Hi\u1ec7p h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u1eabn \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t HLV n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y. Theo \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm Wenger nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u00f3 HLV Wenger l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Wenger t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 m\u00f9a 1995/96 \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft CLB Nagoya Grampus Eight c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, sau khi r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u00f4ng m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Arsenal.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Wenger\" title=\"Wenger\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/15/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-16-chu-tu-wenger-se-thay-the-zidane.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Wenger c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i l\u1edbn, Iniesta v\u00e0 Fernando Torres \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc x\u1ee9 s\u1edf m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi m\u1ecdc \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t cao \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u00f4ng Wenger d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110TQG n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Trung Qu\u1ed1c nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4403","checkdouble":"191651"},{"date":"11:06 20/07","title":"Chelsea ch\u1ed1t 3 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean thay th\u1ebf Courtois","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/7/chelsea-chot-3-ung-vien-thay-the-courois.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Thibaut Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid, Chelsea s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf. Hi\u1ec7n The Blues \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean thay th\u1ebf th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Courtois s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKeylor Navas v\u1eabn \u0111ang ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, song n\u0103m nay anh \u0111\u00e3 32 tu\u1ed5i, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tr\u1ebb h\u01a1n. Thibaut Courtois \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Los Blancos, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau Chelsea nh\u1eafm n\u1ebfu Thibaut Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau Chelsea nh\u1eafm n\u1ebfu Thibaut Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/7/chelsea-chot-3-ung-vien-thay-the-courois.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Thibaut Courtois s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Courtois \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb dao \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha, anh r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bernabeu. C\u00e1c con c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang \u1edf th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Madrid, b\u1edfi v\u1eady anh r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i TBN \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1ea7n g\u0169i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c con c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1edbi Anh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n. Don Balon kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u euro.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Courtois v\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Real kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i chi qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea ch\u1ed1t ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf cho Courtois</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Thibaut Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid, Chelsea s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf. Hi\u1ec7n The Blues \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean thay th\u1ebf th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool mua Gianluigi Donnarumma\" title=\"Liverpool mua Gianluigi Donnarumma\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/28/Milan-muon-doi-Donnarumma-lay-Morata-cua-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Gianluigi Donnarumma \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea nh\u1eafm thay Courtois</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nEvening Standard kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh danh s\u00e1ch 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Chelsea bao g\u1ed3m Donnarumma c\u1ee7a AC Milan, Kasper Schmeichel c\u1ee7a\u00a0Leicester City v\u00e0 Petr Cech c\u1ee7a Arsenal.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00f4m qua, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/khong-the-gay-soc-vu-alisson-chelsea-chuyen-huong-sang-donnarumma-172-191596.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Donnarumma</span>, n\u1ebfu AC Milan kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd h\u1ecd s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Kasper Schmeichel. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Leicester.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u201cB\u1ea7y c\u00e1o\u201d gi\u1eef th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1 Chelsea s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i mua l\u1ea1i Petr Cech, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd tin t\u01b0\u1edfng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 1 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u0103m t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111ang r\u1ea5t hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Donnarumma, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng d\u00f9ng Alvaro Morata trao \u0111\u1ed5i. The Blues s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan nh\u1ea3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 19 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4402","checkdouble":"191653"},{"date":"11:28 20/07","title":"\"H\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\" Barca chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/29/lucas-digne-chuan-bi-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barca b\u00e1n Lucas Digne n\u1ebfu thu v\u1ec1 16 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u1edf h\u1eefu ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang d\u1ea7n l\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n. Mirror kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Everton l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Lucas Digne</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Lucas Digne kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Barca. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Camp Nou v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2016 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca b\u00e1n Lucas Digne cho Everton v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 16 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Barca b\u00e1n Lucas Digne cho Everton v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 16 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/27/Barca-ban-Lucas-Digne-cho-Everton-voi-gia-16-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca b\u00e1n Digne v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 16 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Alba \u1edf h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i, nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t hi\u1ebfm hoi. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 8 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf La Liga, nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n anh c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, Barca \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Theo \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan s\u1ebd b\u00e1n Digne n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o ch\u1ecbu chi ra 16 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/bayern-munich-muon-rut-ruot-barca-180-187783.html\" target=\"_blank\">Bayern Munich mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Lucas Digne</span>, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 12 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Lucas Digne s\u1eafp c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Digne cho Bayern b\u1edfi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c n\u1eb7ng, \u0111\u1ed9i \u0110KV\u0110 La Liga \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ee7 16 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Everton d\u00f9 gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Digne nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf b\u1edfi chi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Barca y\u00eau c\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i Barca chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"H\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i Barca chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/lucas-digne-chuan-bi-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Everton s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Lucas Digne</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMundo Deportivo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Barca b\u00e1n Lucas Digne cho Everton v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 16 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 trong tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi. Everton \u0111ang t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho Leighton Baines, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 16 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh chi ra nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn. D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf s\u00e2n Camp Nou nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh Digne ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Everton.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Digne, Andre Gomes, Rafinha, Marlon v\u00e0 Aleix Vidal l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi Camp Nou \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4401","checkdouble":"191654"},{"date":"11:35 20/07","title":"Alisson Becker: Gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 t\u00e2n binh Liverpool \u2013 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/20/alisson-becker-giai-ma-tan-binh-liverpool-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson Becker t\u1eeb AS Roma v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 67 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, bi\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i sao Brazil tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng Hai \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m nay, khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 c\u01a1n \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u trong khung th\u00e0nh s\u00e2n Anfield, Jurgen Klopp b\u00ecnh th\u1ea3n tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi: \u201cGi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng tri\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3, t\u1ed1i \u0111a nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 trong tay. C\u00e1c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng, trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 kh\u1eafc h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y.\u201d</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool mua Alisson Gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool mua Alisson Gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/27/Liverpool-mua-Alisson-Giai-ma-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Loris Karius kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i qu\u00e1 t\u1ed3i, nh\u01b0ng anh l\u1ea1i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \"ng\u00e1o\" ch\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00fd mu\u00f4n thu\u1edf, anh kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee9 mu\u1ed1n g\u00ec l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ea5y. Th\u1ebf l\u00e0 tr\u00f4i \u0111i n\u0103m th\u00e1ng, sau m\u1ed9t <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/tham-hoa-loris-karius-kiem-cui-9-thang-thieu-90-phut-184-187196.html\" target=\"_blank\">tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda c\u1ee7a Loris Karius</span> v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Brazil, Liverpool ph\u00e1 k\u00e9t 67 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 x\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed5 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00ec Alisson Becker, ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb AS Roma.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1ed3i d\u00e0o t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh sau nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i tham d\u1ef1 Champions League, c\u1ed9ng h\u01b0\u1edfng ng\u00e2n qu\u1ef9 d\u01b0 d\u1ea3 nh\u1edd th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 b\u00e1n Philippe Coutinho cho Barcelona, Liverpool ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd t\u1ef1 tin \u00edt nh\u1ea5t c\u1ea1nh tranh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u0103m v\u1eeba qua, ngu\u1ed3n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00f4 bi\u00ean c\u1ee7a Liverpool n\u1eb1m \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng pressing, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a tam t\u1ea5u t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t hai c\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Mohamed Salah v\u00e0 Sadio Mane. Tuy nhi\u00ean gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ecf\u00a0 v\u00f9ng Merseyside s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng h\u01a1n \u1edf m\u1ed9t tr\u1ee5c d\u1ecdc x\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee9ng c\u00e1p v\u00e0 v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc, v\u1edbi Virgil Van Dijk, Naby Keita v\u00e0 Fabinho c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Alisson.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-kich-no-bom-tan-alisson-172-191632.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/Premier-League-chiem-nua-doi-hinh-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-kich-no-bom-tan-alisson-172-191632.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Liverpool k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n Alisson</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Alisson gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Alisson<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf m\u00e0 n\u00f3i, Alisson h\u1eb5n c\u00f2n t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i thi\u1ebfu kinh nghi\u1ec7m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00ean g\u00e2y h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa, k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng cho c\u00e1c C\u0110V Liverpool h\u01a1n l\u00e0 \u00e2u lo, \u00e1i ng\u1ea1i. 26 tu\u1ed5i, Alisson c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n \u1edf Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t CLB, v\u1eady m\u00e0 anh kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 th\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i s\u1edbm l\u1ecdt m\u1eaft xanh c\u1ee7a ngay c\u1ea3 si\u00eau \u0111\u1ea1i gia Real Madrid.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a Alisson v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu anh t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u duy tr\u00ec ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng, Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 cho m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady cho c\u1ea3 th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 ti\u1ebfp theo \u0111\u00e2y, bi\u1ebfn 67 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh con s\u1ed1 nh\u1ecf b\u00e9, r\u1ebb b\u00e8o.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson Becker Gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 t\u00e2n binh Liverpool \u2013 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Alisson Becker Gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 t\u00e2n binh Liverpool \u2013 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/11/Alisson-Becker-Giai-ma-tan-binh-Liverpool-\u2013-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>V\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u00e0 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, Alisson \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh cho Brazil \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alisson ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, sinh tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u1edf bang Rio Grande do Sul v\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nu\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng b\u1edfi CLB Internacional. M\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 83 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ee9ng khung g\u1ed7 khi gia nh\u1eadp Roma n\u0103m 2016, Alisson ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Wojciech Szczesny c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf Serie A. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn khi c\u1ef1u ng\u00f4i sao Arsenal ra \u0111i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus t\u1eeb m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, c\u1edd m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn tay Alisson v\u00e0 anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ph\u1ea5t n\u00f3, v\u1edbi 49 tr\u1eadn b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 ba Serie A c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 gi\u00e0nh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil tr\u00ecu m\u1ebfn \u0111\u1eb7t bi\u1ec7t danh \u201cgoleiro gato\u201d, d\u1ecbch ra ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 \u201cch\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eb9p trai\u201d, v\u1eady nh\u01b0ng Alisson kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1eabu qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ngh\u1ec1 tay tr\u00e1i ki\u1ebfm th\u00eam thu nh\u1eadp, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed m\u1ed9t m\u1ef1c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n c\u01a1n th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111\u00e0 th\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a anh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<table cellpacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"padding:10px 0px;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\" width=\"44px\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"/content/images/s1.png\" alt=\"comment left\" width=\"44px\"></td>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px;\">\r\n            <div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>Alisson \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 h\u01a1n th\u1ebf nhi\u1ec1u. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c v\u1ec1 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. \u0110\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 coi Alisson nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t Messi trong khung th\u00e0nh, ai \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i li\u00ean t\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng v\u1ec1 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Dino Zoff.</em></div>\r\n            <span style=\"color: #8bc53f; float: right;\"><em>Roberto Negrisolo, c\u1ef1u HLV th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Roma.</em></span></td>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\" width=\"44px\"><img src=\"/content/images/s2.png\" alt=\"comment right\" width=\"44px\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson gia nhap Liverpool\" title=\"Alisson gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/Premier-League-chiem-nua-doi-hinh-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool mua Alisson v\u00e0 ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fd do Liverpool ph\u00e1 k\u00e9t v\u00ec Alisson<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi nghi\u1ec5m nhi\u00ean t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i m\u1ed7i khi c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh: Li\u1ec7u r\u1eb1ng anh ta c\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n c\u00f9ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed hay kh\u00f4ng? Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y v\u1edbi Liverpool mua Alisson, c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi d\u00f5ng d\u1ea1c \u2013 C\u00f3, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00f3!<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng cho Loris Karius v\u00e0 Simon Mignolet r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p \u1edf Anfield kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i, v\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng \u00edt m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n trong khung g\u1ed7, nh\u01b0ng quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u thi\u1ebfu t\u00ednh \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 th\u1eeba nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m ng\u1edb ng\u1ea9n nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ebft ch\u00f3c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"nhung con so so sanh Alisson voi Karius\" title=\"nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 so s\u00e1nh Alisson v\u1edbi Karius\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/day-nhung-con-so-cho-thay-su-ap-dao-cua-alisson-voi-karius.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool mua Alisson, t\u00e2n binh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda Karius</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alisson c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u b\u1eb1ng hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1edbi, nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 l\u1ec7 thu\u1ed9c nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 n\u00f3i chung c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3. Quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t, Alisson s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c th\u00edch nghi, h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Liverpool khi Roma c\u1ee7a anh ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t Serie A m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c C\u0110V Liverpool s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 c\u00e0ng th\u00eam ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch khi bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng Alisson ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua. Kh\u00e1 tuy\u1ec7t n\u1ebfu th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u v\u1edbt nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng, nh\u01b0 David De Gea c\u1ee7a Manchester United, nh\u01b0ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u cho m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p Champions League ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p \u0111\u00e1nh r\u01a1i \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e2y, trong t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh h\u01a1n 20 tr\u1eadn \u1edf n\u0103m gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Alisson ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ecbu x\u1ebfp sau De Gea v\u00e0 Jan Oblak c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"De Gea va Alisson\" title=\"De Gea va Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/De-Gea-va-Alisson.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool mua Alisson kh\u00f4ng thua g\u00ec De Gea c\u1ee7a Man Utd</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span class=\"mfirst-letter\"><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#333333\">\u0110\u1ea5y l\u00e0 Roma ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1n gi\u00e1 cao b\u1eb1ng Man Utd hay Atletico v\u00e0 k\u1ec3 ra m\u00e0 n\u00f3i, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 n\u00f3i l\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec1u, khi n\u00f3 c\u00f2n ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o ki\u1ec3u d\u1ea1ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m khung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. <o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span class=\"mfirst-letter\"><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#333333\">V\u00ed d\u1ee5 nh\u01b0 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t Atletico Madrid b\u1eadc th\u1ea7y ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 bu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u1ea3i s\u00fat xa c\u1ea7u may t\u1eeb ngo\u00e0i v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba h\u00f2ng gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa b\u1ebf t\u1eafc, Oblak hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng c\u1ee9u thua nh\u1eefng pha b\u00f3ng k\u00e9m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n.<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, phong c\u00e1ch ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Liverpool ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ngh\u1ecbch \u0111\u1ea3o v\u1edbi Atletico. \u0110\u00f3 lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u01a1ng pressing t\u1eeb xa thay v\u00ec co c\u1ee5m khu v\u1ef1c. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 con dao hai l\u01b0\u1ee1i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ea9y th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Jurgen Klopp v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf hi\u1ec3m ngh\u00e8o v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ed1ng tr\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb1ng sau ph\u00f2ng tuy\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n v\u1edbi s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng gi\u1ea3i nguy trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng 1v1.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-nhung-con-so-cho-thay-su-ap-dao-cua-alisson-voi-karius-172-191639.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/day-nhung-con-so-cho-thay-su-ap-dao-cua-alisson-voi-karius.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-nhung-con-so-cho-thay-su-ap-dao-cua-alisson-voi-karius-172-191639.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a Alisson v\u1edbi Karius</span><br>\r\nC\u00f9ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 bom t\u1ea5n 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y trang th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Opta \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 so s\u00e1nh Alisson v\u1edbi Karius.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Alisson x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng 67 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi hay kh\u00f4ng?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng Ederson hay c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Thibaut Courtois c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 b\u1eb1ng ph\u00e2n n\u1eeda trong th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ng\u00e0y nay (kho\u1ea3ng 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng), v\u1eady n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng \u00edt \u00fd ki\u1ebfn c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf cho r\u1eb1ng Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 mua \u0111\u1eaft Alisson. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, h\u1ecd d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 b\u1eb5ng qu\u00ean r\u1eb1ng Courtois ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea, trong khi ch\u00ednh Alisson khi\u1ebfn Ederson, ch\u1ed1t ch\u1eb7n s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 vua n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh Man City, ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn ph\u1eadn d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Brazil.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu Alisson ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y s\u1ebd nhanh ch\u00f3ng r\u01a1i v\u00e0o qu\u00ean l\u00e3ng. Liverpool c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 gia c\u1ed1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n, v\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0m v\u1eady nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ebd hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean. Kh\u00e1 kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed soi m\u00f3i \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a Alisson.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson cua Liverpool\" title=\"Alisson cua Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/Alisson-cua-Liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool mua Alisson v\u00e0 ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i n\u00e0y th\u00ec m\u1ea5t c\u00e1i kia, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00ean b\u00e0n c\u00e2n so s\u00e1nh t\u01b0\u01a1ng quan gi\u1eefa kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 khu v\u1ef1c c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba v\u00e0 \u1ee9ng ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t 1v1. \u0110\u01a1n c\u1eed, nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n cao r\u00e1o nh\u01b0 Courtois hay Petr Cech c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1eed l\u00fd t\u1ed1t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t c\u00e1nh v\u00e0 b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng n\u00f3i chung, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd thi\u1ebfu \u0111i s\u1ef1 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng d\u00e2ng cao nh\u01b0 Hugo Lloris hay Marc-Andre ter Stegen.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Alisson th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n v\u1edbi th\u1ebf m\u1ea1nh n\u1eb1m \u1edf c\u1ea3 hai, \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u1edf c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t kho\u1ea3n ch\u1ed1ng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ed1n d\u0129 lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 c\u01a1n \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u kinh ni\u00ean c\u1ee7a Liverpool, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil s\u1ebd c\u00f2n ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c trong vi\u1ec7c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u00e2ng cao \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eb7t, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u01a1i m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Liverpool mua Alisson v\u00e0 ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi:<br>\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/alisson-noi-gi-khi-chinh-thuc-gia-nhap-liverpool-172-191633.html\">Alisson n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-chia-se-nguyen-nhan-bien-alisson-thanh-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-172-191634.html\">Klopp chia s\u1ebb nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n bi\u1ebfn Alisson th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/voi-alisson-premier-league-chiem-tron-hang-thu-dat-gia-nhat-hanh-tinh-172-191635.html\">V\u1edbi Alisson, Premier League chi\u1ebfm tr\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4400","checkdouble":"191660"},{"date":"07:03 20/07","title":"C\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, th\u1ea7y Park n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/cong-bo-danh-sach-dt-olympic-viet-nam-thay-park-noi-ve-co-hoi-cua-thu-mon-bui-tien-dung.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, HLV Park Hang Seo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u1eabn chia \u0111\u1ec1u cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh n\u1ebfu th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t.</h2><h2>Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u00e1ng 19/7, t\u1ea1i tr\u1ee5 s\u1edf L\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra l\u1ec5 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 Gi\u1ea3i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng 2018 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tham d\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a 4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng bao g\u1ed3m 23 VI\u1ec7t Nam, U23 Uzbekistan, U23 Oman v\u00e0 U23 Palestine. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng trong bu\u1ed5i l\u1ec5 n\u00e0y, VFF \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch t\u1eadp trung \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Trong s\u1ed1 30 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi t\u1eadp trung l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0a ra c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt ng\u00e0y. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3i qua qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n v\u00e0 th\u1eed th\u00e1ch n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap HLV Park Hang Seo t\u00ecm ra nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Park Hang Seo\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/cong-bo-danh-sach-dt-olympic-viet-nam-thay-park-noi-ve-co-hoi-cua-thu-mon-bui-tien-dung.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho m\u1ecdi tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u00e0i n\u0103ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, HLV Park Hang Seo cho bi\u1ebft s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a ra danh s\u00e1ch 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 18 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c cho hay: &ldquo;Sau c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0o c\u00e1c ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u00f9ng 3,5,7/8 th\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Asiad 2018 v\u00e0o s\u00e1ng m\u00f9ng 7. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 t\u1eebng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0a ra k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn r\u1eb1ng, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i&rdquo;.</p>\r\n<h2>HLV Park Hang Seo m\u1edf ra hy v\u1ecdng cho B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn ai gi\u1eefa hai g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nay l\u00e0 \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u00e0 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, \u00f4ng Park n\u00f3i th\u00eam: &ldquo;T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ch\u1ed1t danh s\u00e1ch v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 07/08&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV h\u1ecd Park c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, \u00e1p l\u1ef1c t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a NHM v\u1edbi to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn do v\u1eady \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch cao nh\u1ea5t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u0169ng th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn chia s\u1ebb ASIAD 2018 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t so v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i U23 Ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 v\u1eeba qua b\u1edfi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf n\u00ean m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n do \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th\u00eam 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i. Do v\u1eady, \u00e1p l\u1ef1c l\u00e0 s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1edbi t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00ean h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ba tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u &lsquo;th\u1eed l\u1eeda&rsquo; c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 U23 Palestine, U23 Oman v\u00e0 U23 Uzbekistan s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 03/08-07/08 t\u1ea1i SV\u0110 M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Danh sach tap trung DT Olympic Viet Nam 2018\" title=\"Danh s\u00e1ch t\u1eadp trung \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/DS-U23-QG_update.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Danh s\u00e1ch t\u1eadp trung \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-dat-muc-tieu-cho-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018-168-191537.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/hlv-park-hang-seo-dat-muc-tieu-cho-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-dat-muc-tieu-cho-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018-168-191537.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp c\u1ee7a VFF chi\u1ec1u 18/7, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-guong-mat-bi-hlv-park-hang-seo-bo-quen-tai-asiad-2018-168-191462.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2015/10/1/hang-thu-dtvn-can-lam-bong-dang-mot-nhu-thanh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-guong-mat-bi-hlv-park-hang-seo-bo-quen-tai-asiad-2018-168-191462.html\">Nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t b\u1ecb HLV Park Hang Seo &lsquo;b\u1ecf qu\u00ean&rsquo; t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nL\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch s\u01a1 b\u1ed9 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean k\u00e9m duy\u00ean ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp \u1edf gi\u1ea3i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tien-dung-thua-nhan-kho-canh-tranh-voi-van-lam-tai-asiad-2018-168-191517.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/5/tien-dung-thua-nhan-kho-canh-tranh-voi-van-lam-tai-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tien-dung-thua-nhan-kho-canh-tranh-voi-van-lam-tai-asiad-2018-168-191517.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e0n anh \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm nh\u01b0ng anh s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4399","checkdouble":"191597"},{"date":"08:05 20/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 20/7: Real Madrid ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1eb7t gi\u00e1 Hazard","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/15/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-207-real-madrid-chinh-thuc-dat-gia-hazard.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 20/7.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nReal Madrid ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1eb7t gi\u00e1 Hazard<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed T\u00e2y Ban Nha, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Real s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 Chelsea v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 B\u1ea3y tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb cho Hazard. M\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 ban \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00e0 Los Blancos chi tr\u1ea3 l\u00e0 125 tri\u1ec7u euro, v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u1edbn The Blues s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, CLB Ho\u00e0ng gia c\u0169ng ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n Thibaut Courtois sau khi ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 35 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 20/7\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 207 Real Madrid ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1eb7t gi\u00e1 Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-207-Real-Madrid-chinh-thuc-dat-gia-Hazard-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 20/7: Real mu\u1ed1n mua b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Eden Hazard</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>Man City l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u1ed1ng c\u1ed5 Sterling<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 2 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Man City. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu anh kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn gia h\u1ea1n, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad s\u1ebd chia tay Sterling trong v\u00f2ng 12 th\u00e1ng t\u1edbi.&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>&ldquo;Gi\u00e1o s\u01b0&rdquo; nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb Nh\u1eadt<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, L\u0110B\u0110 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eddi HLV Arsene Wenger d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia. T\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi m\u1ecdc ch\u1ec9 d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0110T B\u1ec9, nh\u01b0ng g\u00e2y ti\u1ebfng vang l\u1edbn khi d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi 2 b\u00e0n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao Juve<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, trung v\u1ec7 <span href=\"http://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-sap-cong-bo-tan-binh-thu-2-tri-gia-36-trieu-bang-172-191548.html\" target=\"_blank\">Daniele Rugani s\u1ebd gia nh\u1eadp The Blues</span> trong th\u1eddi gian s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t, sau khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 44,2 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng (bao g\u1ed3m ph\u1ee5 ph\u00ed) c\u00f9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 77 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n. \u0110\u1ec3 th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7, B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0 th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn s\u00e1t Diego Godin &ndash; trung v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00f3n tin vui tr\u00ean TTCN<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/day-dau-hieu-cho-thay-leicester-sap-co-danny-ward-172-191617.html\" target=\"_blank\">Leicester \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd chi ra 12,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Danny Ward</span> &ndash; \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Kasper Schmeichel, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea theo s\u00e1t \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Courtois.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c s\u1edf h\u1eefu th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-kich-no-bom-tan-alisson-172-191632.html\" target=\"_blank\">The Kop \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alisson Becker t\u1eeb AS Roma</span>, sau khi ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi tr\u1ea3 56 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u00f9ng 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ph\u1ee5 ph\u00ed, khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 207 Real Madrid ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1eb7t gi\u00e1 Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 207 Real Madrid ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1eb7t gi\u00e1 Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-207-Real-Madrid-chinh-thuc-dat-gia-Hazard-hinh-anh-2.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/\" title=\"bong da\" type=\"bong da\">b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span> s\u00e1ng 20/7: Alisson gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>M.U nh\u1eadn tin vui t\u1eeb Sanchez</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd c\u1ee7a M\u1ef9, cho ph\u00e9p anh t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 tour du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Mourinho lo ng\u1ea1i Alexis Sanchez kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00ec r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i visa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4398","checkdouble":"191640"}]}